      <!-- ===== JANUARY 2026 ===== -->
      <section class="prog-month" id="janvier">
        <h2 class="prog-month-title">January 2026</h2>

        <article class="prog-event">
          <div class="prog-event-date">
            <span class="prog-event-day">Saturday</span>
            <span class="prog-event-num">31 January</span>
            <span class="prog-event-time">10am - 1pm</span>
          </div>
          <div class="prog-event-body">
            <p class="prog-event-category">Workshop with Rose</p>
            <h3>Art of movement with the Feldenkrais Method — Your back in motion!</h3>
            <p>Do you suffer from neck tension, lower back pain, or difficulty bending or turning your head? This workshop is for you! During this morning session, you will practise simple, gentle and unusual movements: feel and develop the richness of your spinal possibilities, to restore suppleness and vitality to your back. An invitation to rediscover a free, alive back and a more fluid daily life!</p>
            <div class="prog-event-meta">
              <span class="prog-event-price">35 EUR + 5 EUR annual membership</span>
              <span class="prog-event-contact"><a href="mailto:rosegiovannini@free.fr">rosegiovannini@free.fr</a> — <a href="http://www.rosegiovannini.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">rosegiovannini.com</a></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="prog-event">
          <div class="prog-event-date">
            <span class="prog-event-day">Saturday</span>
            <span class="prog-event-num">31 January</span>
            <span class="prog-event-time">2pm - 4pm</span>
          </div>
          <div class="prog-event-body">
            <p class="prog-event-category">Workshop with Rose</p>
            <h3>1, 2, 3 Sleep!</h3>
            <p>Come and discover an innovative system to improve your sleep!</p>
            <p>Sleep is a vital need... but sometimes it eludes us. Long restless nights, agitation, thoughts going round in circles... Sound familiar?</p>
            <p>The Sounder Sleep System, created by Michael Krugman, a Feldenkrais practitioner, is a gentle yet powerful technique based on breathing and mini-movements.</p>
            <p>A clear presentation of the system, a 30-minute guided practice, and a friendly chat over a Herbarius herbal tea!</p>
            <div class="prog-event-meta">
              <span class="prog-event-price">Free</span>
              <span class="prog-event-contact"><a href="mailto:rosegiovannini@free.fr">rosegiovannini@free.fr</a> — <a href="http://www.rosegiovannini.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">rosegiovannini.com</a></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </section>

